No, Dandruff does not go away with Oiling, Washing your Hair Everyday or even Anti-Dandruff Shampoos
•
•
There are so many types of dandruff that need to be identified before treating. Dry Scalp Dandruff is so much different than Oily Scalp Dandruff & you might be treating it all wrong. But this one hack can work on all scalp types and no matter the reason for dandruff.....

Take any glycolic acid suitable for hair (eg-@theordinary and @beminimalist__ ) and clean your scalp thoroughly using a q-tip like in video or using a cotton pad. Trust me, it cleans your scalp from any dirt, pollution or buildup like no other product can. Then you can continue with your normal wash routine.
You can do this anytime in the day. Just don’t forget to do a patch test before.

Some bonds are made not just by blood, but by memories, moments, and unconditional love — that’s what my cousins mean to me. From childhood mischief to grown-up conversations, from fun games to late-night heart-to-hearts, we’ve grown together in ways only we can understand. They’ve seen my unfiltered self, held my hand during my lows, and celebrated my every little win like their own. Being with them feels like home — safe, familiar, full of laughter and love. Time flies when we’re together, but the moments we share stay with me forever. No matter where life takes us, this bond will always be my anchor. Cousins are our first best friends, our forever cheerleaders, and the keepers of our childhood stories. Blessed beyond words to have them in my life.❤️
